data.description:
4 MASTER BEDROOMS, 4.5 BATH, 3300 SF LARGE HOME ON A CUL-DE-SAC STREET. JACCUZI AND SOAKING TUB. 2 STONE WOOD BURNING FIRE PLACES. HUGE 2 TIER DECK. 2 ZONe heating and air conditioning (2023). Tankless gas water heater (2023). Roof (2022). Gas and electric connection options for cooking range and dryer. 3 CAR OVER SIZED GARAGE WITH SIX WINDOWS AND ELECTRIC OPENERS. 2”x6” CONSTRUCTION WITH STUCCO ALL AROUND. LARGE LAUNDRY ROOM WITH CABINETS. NEW DISH WASHER (2022). UPGRADED POWDER ROOM (2020). UPGRADED KITCHEN WITH GRANITE COUNTER TOPS AND HUGE ISLAND (2012).
UNDER GROUND OIL TABKS HAS BEEN REMOVED AND. ALL SOIL REMEDIATION WORK COMPLETED AS PER NJDEP REQUIREMENNTS. ALL WORK IS APPROVED BY NJDEP AND OBTAINED NFA (NO FURTHER ACTION) LETTER FROM NJDEP. Oil heater and water heater and oil tank have been removed and replaced with new gas heater and new tankless water heater.
